{"tid":931644,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得專營巴士好應該整分段收費，唔好比鐵路獨大","createTime":"2018-12-07T07:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T08:44:09.000Z","uid":11598,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59e2706f58db882735cd196b8bbed097f66b8be8","tid":931644,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"而家成個發展方向都係傾向鐵路，起鐵路沿線運吉署就一路cut巴士線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係問題係有時只不過係想去區內附近 搭程巴士好方便 但係要比全程車資<br />\n實在太荒謬 如果可以學新加坡／輕鐵咁玩分段收費／收費區 上車落車計錢<br />\n相信專營巴士競爭力會更加高，而且某程度可以釋放返啲鐵路載客量 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e03269b15709ef0b57d8fa551a76b9f3e8702f6","tid":931644,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d26105685e120950e1b0cd3f9836953b5815bad","tid":931644,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e03269b15709ef0b57d8fa551a76b9f3e8702f6","tid":931644,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309b6386acf72dea09dcce137c7d4c19beb68ec3","tid":931644,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:24:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7e09a84dfd1e2590c49b54f4200a75cdd4424c6","tid":931644,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"309b6386acf72dea09dcce137c7d4c19beb68ec3","tid":931644,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7d26105685e120950e1b0cd3f9836953b5815bad","tid":931644,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e03269b15709ef0b57d8fa551a76b9f3e8702f6","tid":931644,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,